00:40:55.660 --> 00:41:12.500
Maria Silva: Yeah, I would also add, this is a more EL topic, but I would say for repricings, it's also very important for us to be able to provide such a network sooner rather than later. Repricings will have a big impact on many of DApps, and they need to kind of

